<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 - Page Not Found</title>
     <!-- tab logo -->
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/images/logo/tabLogo.png">
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
            background: #f7f7f7;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: #333;
        }
        
        .container {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            max-width: 600px;
        }
        
        .error-code {
            font-size: 120px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ff6b6b, #4ecdc4);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            line-height: 1;
        }
        
        .error-message {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin: 1rem 0;
            color: #555;
        }
        
        .error-description {
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        
        .home-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ff6b6b, #4ecdc4);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }
        
        .home-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        
        .astronaut {
            font-size: 100px;
            animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        @keyframes float {
            0% { transform: translateY(0px); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-20px); }
            100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="astronaut">üë®‚ÄçüöÄ</div>
        <h1 class="error-code">404</h1>
        <h2 class="error-message"> we have a problem!</h2>
        <p class="error-description">
            The page you're looking for has floated off into space or never existed in the first place.
            Don't worry though, you can always return to safety by clicking the button below.
        </p>
        <a href="/" class="home-button">Return Home</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>